                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t17930911-44-defend506 t17930911-44-punish242"></join>
               Death
            </rs>. (Aged 22.)</p>
               <p>Tried by the second Middlesex Jury before Mr. Justice HEATH.</p>
